OverSampling¶

In [577]:
s=SMOTE(sampling_strategy=0.7) 
X,y=s.fit_resample(X,y)

Feature Selection¶

In [578]:
extra_tree_forest = ExtraTreesClassifier(n_estimators =8,
                                        criterion ='entropy', max_features = 7)
extra_tree_forest.fit(X, y)
feature_importance = pd.Series(extra_tree_forest.feature_importances_, index=X.columns)
In [579]:
X=X[list(feature_importance.nlargest(22).index)]

Splitting into Train and Test¶

Xtrain,Xtest,Ytrain,Ytest=train_test_split(X,y,test_size=0.2,random_state=5)

Normaliation¶

In [580]:
s=MinMaxScaler() 
s.fit(Xtrain[list(Xtrain.columns)]) 
Xtrain[list(Xtrain.columns)]=s.transform(Xtrain[list(Xtrain.columns)]) 
Xtest[list(Xtrain.columns)]=s.transform(Xtest[list(Xtrain.columns)])

Model Building¶

In [586]:
Lc=LogisticRegression(tol=0.01,solver="liblinear",C=0.75,max_iter=70,penalty="l1") 
Dt=DecisionTreeClassifier(criterion="entropy",max_depth=15,min_samples_split=7) 
Rf=RandomForestClassifier(n_estimators=85,criterion="entropy",max_depth=10,min_samples_split=6)
In [587]:
Lc.fit(Xtrain,Ytrain) 
Dt.fit(Xtrain,Ytrain) 
Rf.fit(Xtrain,Ytrain) 
ypred1=Lc.predict(Xtest)
ypred2=Dt.predict(Xtest) 
ypred3=Rf.predict(Xtest)
